<section class="statement" id="hvem">
  <div class="wrap statement-inner">
    <span class="eyebrow">
      <span data-da>Hvem arbejder jeg med?</span><span data-en>Who works with me?</span>
    </span>
    <p class="statement-text" data-da>
      <span class="hl">De mennesker, jeg arbejder med, er præcis det — mennesker. Du behøver
      ikke imponere mig, og du behøver ikke møde op med svarene. Måske har du
      et mål for øje, eller bare noget, der stille nager. Uanset hvad er det
      rigeligt til, at vi kan begynde.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="statement-text" data-en>
      <span class="hl">The people I work with are just that — people. You don't need to impress
      me, and you don't need to arrive with the answers. You might have a goal
      in mind, or just something quietly niggling. Either way, that's enough
      for us to start with.</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
